Class EmergencyDept

  • java.lang.Object
    • simergy.core.system.EmergencyDept
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class EmergencyDept
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Class EmergencyDept. This is the most important class of the core. One instance of this class contains all the informations, workflows and description of the ED.

        public EmergencyDept()

      • generateResources

        public static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.util.ArrayList<Resource>> generateResources()
        Generates the HashMap containing all the resources. The index is made of Strings representing a canonical type of the resource.
        Returns:
        the hash map containing all the ED's resources.

      • update

        public void update()
        Updates the time in the ED. Then it checks for a new patient arrival. Then all the workflows are updated.
        See Also:
        TimeMachine.toNextTime(), Workflow.update()
